Note on naming conventions:
[square brackets]: Group a number of entities by application/service name. Useful as Archi can struggle with organising their components.
<<Stereotypes>>: Where an Archimate element has been overloaded, use UML-like stereotypes to enable sub-types. http://pubs.opengroup.org/architecture/archimate3-doc/chap15.html
